CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 6, 1946, pg. 25, reads: "YMCA Tournament Champions - Upper left: The 'Y' Vets are shown receiving the beautiful trophy given by the Pittsburgh Courier for the senior title. They are, left to right: Coach Carson, Adams, Ford, Myers, Fowler, Pollard, Ches Washington making the presentation, Atkins, Lewis, and Ritter... - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of YMCA Vets basketball team, including coach Carson on left, and players, including Ernest Myers squatting on left, and Adams, Ford, Fowler, Pollard, Atkins, Lewis, and Ritter, posed in gymnasium
